==== Countdown Plugin Changelog ====

2019-01-13  Luis Machuca Bezzaza

    * Version: 2.6.
    * syntax.php: Removed getInfo() in favor of DW native.
    * syntax.php: PHP >= 7.0 function prototype warnings fixed by Stefan Huehner.
    * The plugin is now moved to a version control.

2011-03-07  Luis Machuca Bezzaza 

    * Version: 2.5rc2
    * cleaner code
    * syntax.php: Corrected a "one day remaining" bug as notified in wikipage.
    * syntax.php: Substituted <strong> container by simple <span class...> one.
    * syntax.php: Beta support for business days.
    * syntax.php: Beta support for notifying the server's wall time.
    * syntax.php: Beta support for text renderer.
    * plugin.info.txt: Added.
    * conf/metadata.php: Added.
    * ChangeLog: Added.
    * Added localized plugin description.

2009-12-18  Luis Machuca Bezzaza 

    * Version: 2.5rc
    * Under new management.
    * lang/: Spanish language file <Luis Machuca Bezzaza>.
    * lang/: Brazilian Portuguese language file <Adirson Maguila>.
    * lang/: Czech language file <Roman Å ilar>.
    * syntax.php: Use getLang, getConf interface.
    * syntax.php: Display hr/min in countdown message.

